							<h1 class="tit_01">KẸO GIẢM CÂN, THUỐC GIẢM CÂN, TRÀ GIẢM CÂN,...CÓ GIÚP BẠN GIẢM CÂN KHÔNG?</h1>
							<div class="blog_meta">
								<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
									<tr>
										<td>
											<svg width="10%" height="10%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16 7C16 9.20914 14.2091 11 12 11C9.79086 11 8 9.20914 8 7C8 4.79086 9.79086 3 12 3C14.2091 3 16 4.79086 16 7Z" stroke="#666666" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M12 14C8.13401 14 5 17.134 5 21H19C19 17.134 15.866 14 12 14Z" stroke="#666666" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Võ Thị Anh Trúc</td>
										<td class="txt_right">
											<svg width="10%" height="10%" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M20 10V7C20 5.89543 19.1046 5 18 5H6C4.89543 5 4 5.89543 4 7V10M20 10V19C20 20.1046 19.1046 21 18 21H6C4.89543 21 4 20.1046 4 19V10M20 10H4M8 3V7M16 3V7" stroke="#666666" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><rect x="6" y="12" width="3" height="3" rx="0.5" fill="#666666"/><rect x="10.5" y="12" width="3" height="3" rx="0.5" fill="#666666"/><rect x="15" y="12" width="3" height="3" rx="0.5" fill="#666666"/></svg>
